remarks.format:
  
  
## Remarks  
 Le <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaObjectCollection.Add%2A> méthode attend uniquement <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaExternal> et ses types dérivés (<xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaImport>, <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaInclude>, et <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaRedefine>) en tant que paramètres. L’exemple suivant illustre l’ajout d’un schéma inclus à la <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema.Includes%2A> collection d’un existant <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema> objet.  
  
```vb  
Dim schema As XmlSchema = New XmlSchema()  
  
Dim textReader As XmlTextReader = New XmlTextReader("include.xsd")  
Dim includeSchema As XmlSchema = XmlSchema.Read(textReader, null)  
  
Dim include As XmlSchemaInclude = New XmlSchemaInclude()  
include.Schema = includeSchema;  
schema.Includes.Add(include);  
```  
  
```csharp  
XmlSchema schema = new XmlSchema();  
  
XmlTextReader textReader = new XmlTextReader("include.xsd");  
XmlSchema includeSchema = XmlSchema.Read(textReader, null);  
  
XmlSchemaInclude include = new XmlSchemaInclude();  
include.Schema = includeSchema;  
schema.Includes.Add(include);  
```
